37#include <sys/cdefs.h>
38__RCSID("$NetBSD: error.c,v 1.4 2011/02/12 23:21:32 christos Exp $");
39
40#include <stdio.h>
41
42#include "error.h"
43
44/**
45 * @brief returns error string
46 * @param err error
47 * @return error string
48 */
49const char *
50saslc__error_get_strerror(saslc__error_t *err)
51{
52
53 if (err->err_str == NULL) {
54 switch (err->err_no) {
55 case ERROR_NOMEM:
56 return "no memory available";
57 case ERROR_PARSE:
58 return "parse error";
59 default:
60 return "unknown";
61 }
62 }
63 return err->err_str;
64}
